\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1661656 OP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11094101\charrsid12984966 No. No. No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1779283 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11094101\charrsid12984966 You got married in 1918?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1661656 OP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11094101\charrsid12984966 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1779283 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11094101\charrsid12984966 And then you stayed with your mother in Bryn Gurnus Street?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1661656 OP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11094101\charrsid12984966 For a twelve month.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1779283 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11094101\charrsid12984966 Do you remember why the family moved from Coalyard Row?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1661656 OP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11094101\charrsid12984966 Oh well of course we wanted a bigger house. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1779283 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11094101\charrsid12984966 And Bryn Burnus Street was bigger?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1661656 OP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11094101\charrsid12984966 Yes, and - of course - the - neighbours were very good, an
d - a friend - a great friend of my mother, or my father, came up from Carmarthen, he was a church man, and told my mother, well it's about time you thought - of a - a - bigger house. And my father said, well - we want money for that. Don't worry about th
a
t, he said, I'll give you a start. And this gentleman - from Carmarthen - Owen Williams his name was, lent the money for my father - to start building the house. And a very good man - man, very good he was, and - when it came time when my mother - when we
 
had - she had money to send - down we used to go to Carmarthen, my sisters, older sisters, and they used to take the money down, and I remember my mother saying once that it was a - a Whitsun time, and she had sent my two sisters, older sisters down to pa
y for this and then he said, now take it back, he said, it's Whitsun, and I suppose that your mother will need some clothes for you for Whitsun, so it'll do for me again. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1779283 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11094101\charrsid12984966 How many brothers and sisters did you have?
