Well - really when - we needed clothes you know she'd come. And I remember when she was coming up she'd go to other places but sleeping in our house. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1779283 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11094101\charrsid12984966 And your mother would pay her of course for that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1661656 OP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11094101\charrsid12984966 Oh yes, was having so much a week, but how much I don't remember anyway, but }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
