\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1779283 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11094101\charrsid12984966 Did he ever read to you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1661656 OP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11094101\charrsid12984966 Yes. Or - and learn us verses of course. Verses from the Bible, ready for Sunday school. And my father was - of course he was - he hadn't
 much schooling, my mother hadn't had schooling at all, my mother couldn't read nor write, but my father was, and he was the - he was the one - that taught all the children - the - the - the - when they used to start going to Sunday school, and in our cha
p
el he'd call the plain and my father was up there with all the children, and - well as soon as they were - going to Sunday school, it was my father taught - all those children. And my mother was there always sorry that she hadn't gone with him, that she c
ould have - you know - picked the - the Welsh up, the - well to read and write then, and she was always sorry.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1779283 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11094101\charrsid12984966 So he was really teaching the little ones how to read and write?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1661656 OP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11094101\charrsid12984966 Yes. Yes, that's right.
