Well - I don't remember very much of that really. But we were - we all - helped in the - what we could do really, and my mother was one not to keep us idle, we had to find - we had to do something.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1779283 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11094101\charrsid12984966 I remember my mother saying that her particular job was she had to clean all the shoes.
