\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1779283 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11094101\charrsid12984966 Any other particular job like that you had to do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1661656 OP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11094101\charrsid12984966 Wel
l - we had to wait - they were working then you know on a Saturday, and - we - they'd come home to bath, well you'd have to clean up - after that, really, if they - you know, if they'd be working on Saturday, it would be a long day on Saturday. And I reme
mber one day my mother had gone on holiday I think, and my brother Tom, he was bathing, and I wanted to go somewhere, and he tipped the - the - the tank, you know, the water - or the bath, I don't remember, so I had to clean all that up.
