\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1661656 OP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11094101\charrsid12984966 
Oh yes. Oh yes, yes, and I mean when of course - later when my father came to work to the colliery - colliery - you know, the manager would come to live there o
f course and we thought they were - you know, important people, and the children were counted you know, but the - take the - the - the vicar after - was in - were there, vicars were in school with us you know, they inclined to think that they were - you k
now - higher class than we were, but of course we were all playing together and all that you know.
