\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1661656 OP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11094101\charrsid12984966 Oh my - stand up now and things like that isn't it you know, it is - for someone to sit down and all that isn't it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1779283 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11094101\charrsid12984966 Like for whom?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1661656 OP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11094101\charrsid12984966 Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1779283 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11094101\charrsid12984966 For whom would you have to stand up?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1661656 OP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11094101\charrsid12984966 
Oh well - well wait now then I don't remember - a Mr - no, Mr Price, I don't know - oh he was all right, we had to, you know, one of us. Hi
s wife was - shopkeeper, you know, grocers shop she was, and - a Mr Moses, Thomas from Ygarrow, you know, they always like us to behave when he come but -
