hat's the kind of character he was. Well he was a very good man and didn't believe in - no dances or anything else but he had a very nice daughter, very attractive, and - the - of course being farmers, there was a dance in Maesteg, and of course she had b
e
en invited there and I suppose - whether it's her boyfriend or what I don't know, but anyway she - would like to - she'd like to go and she asked her mother. If she could - if she should go to the dance. And her mother said, you'd better ask your father m
