 dear. So she asked her father, daddy, she said, are you willing for me to go to the dance to Maesteg next Saturday? Yes, yes, Mary, he said, only for you to take your God with you then. Yes, that's the kind of person you know he was, he was a wonderful o
ld man. And many other characters if I could remember you know, but he was - outstanding. Yes, yes, yes.
