Yes, or the hall then, no, you know, it was more like penny readings they used to call them. Yes, and I remember - they used to ask you know - come up and ask and - ask you questions. And - I won't name you will I - li
ke that, and my brother went up, and - the minister asked him to name the - the first four books in the New Testament. And he said - Matthew - Matthew, Mark, Luke and John. Hold this horse 'til I get on. And my mother was furious you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1779283 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11094101\charrsid12984966 They were like little impromptu concerts weren't they?
