Yes, you know, yes, that's right, yes. And I know - oh I used to - I remember there was down in the - in the village too, and - penny readings they used to call you know and - everybody used to go there, an
d they'd show perhaps pictures or something like that you know now and gain. Penny readings, and everybody'd go and try and say of course - older than me, I remember them you know. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1779283 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11094101\charrsid12984966 You paid a penny to go in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1661656 OP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11094101\charrsid12984966 Yes. Yes.
