Well - I don't remember that, but my father - his Bible then - was in - ribbons I know. My father never went to bed without reading a portion of the Bible. But - in his bedroom, you know, he used to -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1779283 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11094101\charrsid12984966 He wouldn't have it with all of you there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1661656 OP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11094101\charrsid12984966 No, I don't remember. Don't remember, but my father - never went to - no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1779283 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11094101\charrsid12984966 Did your father take an interest in politics?
