erals they used to be then, and - my - one of my brothers Bob, he joined the I - ILP I remember, that was of course - I'm getting - I - too - that's too - my brother - my brother joined the ILP in Cwmavon, and - he was said that he'd be broken out of chap
el and all, 'cos his parent - my - you know, they were all saying then - that - the deacons were saying - that - they shouldn't be members of chapel - if they were carrying on like that and all that but -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1779283 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11094101\charrsid12984966 Did they actually break anybody out of chapel?
