l - chapel as I say isn't it, two nights a week isn't it, they were there. Then - friends would call in you know and have a - little chat and all that. Well then my father you know, of course working hard, he'd always go to bed pretty early. Pretty early 
my father.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1779283 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11094101\charrsid12984966 Did your mother have any interests outside the house, the home?
