re us - the - he gets the same. They - stop him and of course he throws money out, and - it same come with us you know then so - my brother of course was with me, he was giving me away. And -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1779283 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11094101\charrsid12984966 Dai is it?
