es. Mm. And the - in some weddings, but that was not while I was, you know, they'd be - shooting, and they'd put - when the train was going then if there was a wedding, they'd put - things under the train you know and it'd be going - of course like bang -
 bangers you know then. Yes, and - there was a crowd of men, they'd go out - with a gun you know and shooting and all that, making a - that's the old time, I remember some - of course then.
