ery superstitious, and she said that we'd - I - I - there'd be no luck if I changed the hat, so I had to wear it anyway because of her. She - she was very superstitious in everything. And she said, now, no - not to change the hat, that it wouldn't be luck
y. So I had the hat made - the same - material as my frock really.
