w about that. And - the school was over there like, and her mother was living here in Colyard Row, in the first - house there you know, and she'd come out to the - to the - top of the - hill - hill lo}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2709787\charrsid12984966 o}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11094101\charrsid12984966 ke}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2709787\charrsid12984966 d}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11094101\charrsid12984966 
 you know, watching us coming out of school, and the
n she'd know of course - and then she'd start shouting, Mevanwy. Mevanwy. Just to show Mevanwy see that - she was watching her that - you know, no harm would come to her then, she'd come out now to meet her. Because we were all on to her.
