\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1779283 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11094101\charrsid12984966 Where did you live after you were married?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1661656 OP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11094101\charrsid12984966 Almost a twelve month with my mother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1779283 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11094101\charrsid12984966 In Bryngurnos Street?
