\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1779283 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11094101\charrsid12984966 To the shop?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1661656 OP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11094101\charrsid12984966 Yes.
