urse as I told - we said before we - used to kill the pigs isn't it, and - it was - ration time then and not much of anything, and as I told you - before that mam used to - share the meat with everybody, but I knew my husband then of course, courting we w
ere then, and I had a steak from the - pork, from the meat, and packed it up and put in my pocket and give it to him that night, but - my mother didn't know of course. I knew he didn't - had - hadn't had much. Mm. Mm.
