nd he never - you know, went to the office to report it or anything you see, and that's what he should have done because he'd have had comp - he's never had - any compensation, and the - the little chap that was working with him, Thomas his name was, I do
n
't remember - he said he remember it quite well, and that his eye was really sore then you know. But he kept on working for a while of course after that see, but I - in time - they - they were on the - both string they say isn't it, so his two eyes went a
fter you see, one first.
