, but - between - between that time you know, well - there's not much between - my Moelwyn and - Nancy see, but I remember that, and he said - well - being that the hadn't seen her could he name here and that's how she's Nancy, after an old person of his 
- you know, an aunt of his - living in the Varteg - Farm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1779283 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11094101\charrsid12984966 You did mention when you moved to Bryngurnos yours was a corner house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1661656 OP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11094101\charrsid12984966 Yes.
