\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1661656 OP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11094101\charrsid12984966 Well - we'd always bee
n, you know, in a corner house, so my mother wanted that. And we were the only - the only house and I suppose that I was - they took me up to see it one time, and I said, oh there's a narrow house that is. It looked of course narrow because it was on its 
