\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1661656 OP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11094101\charrsid12984966 Yes. Yes. Mm. And if mam would go and cook or something perhaps I'd go and try in there you know}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
