 In the frame. Mm. Got to be very accurate really. And - my aunt of course, but my mother came after of course you know, but I was quilting with my mother then. After that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1779283 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11094101\charrsid12984966 You were saying too that a dressmaker would come from Cwmavon and sleep in the house?
