 on the Saturday night he was lecturing, and - she came with us then you know, to the lecture. Mm. And - really - whether you know Philip Jones of course you do don't you, well you know, we - when he came in - when she saw him, ooh, she said, he's startin
g, and she's like that, smiled you know, laughed out really, 'cos she was so impressed to see him, and of course he used to make some faces didn't he. So she was in - very interested in it. Mm.
