Oh yes, singing, oh yes. In front of the house you see, before - you know, in the front of the house, and - sometimes - by walking up, you know - walking for a while. Yes. Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1779283 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11094101\charrsid12984966 And then at the graveside?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1661656 OP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11094101\charrsid12984966 Yes, yes. Yes. A preacher you know like is - like it is you know like now. Service you know, but singing, beautiful singing always.

