Oh no. No. No. Mm. No. Mind there were passengers there of course. But - sometimes of course - say that they'd say now when the competition was, had to be forty or fifty voic
es, well they had to take passengers then. And I remember one time you know they were - we were competing, and - one of these two - or two of these passengers you know now were told to be quiet, and not to sing at all, only pretend you know, but one of th
em shouted of course we were out of competition then. Mm.
